      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يُدَبِّرُ مَمْلُوكَهُ أَ لَهُ أَنْ يَرْجِعَ فِيهِ فَقَالَ \"نَعَمْ هُوَ بِمَنْزِلَةِ اَلْوَصِيَّةِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5565 - Muhammad ibn Abi Umayr narrated from Hisham ibn Al-Hakam, who said:\nI asked Imam (as) about a man who designates his slave for emancipation after his death (mudabbar). Can he revoke this decision?\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, it is like a will.\""
        ]
      }
    },
